    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s totally ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my car, and it has been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-loved and looked after. Whether you're just zipping around town or planning a long weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to hit the road. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
