      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Silver Grey Metallic. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, a masterclass in atmospheric engineering featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement with TMS plates to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throws, sending power through a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is maintained with upgraded bushings, providing the tactile steering feedback these chassis are renowned for. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain harmonics are exceptional. Recent cooling system refresh and VANOS service make this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
