      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver\u2019s car powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels through a GKN-sourced M Variable differential. The chassis has been proactively addressed with subframe reinforcement plates to mitigate fatigue, and the suspension retains its factory-tuned kinematics with refreshed bushings. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including rod bearing clearance and cooling system pressure\u2014are within spec. This is an mechanically sound example optimized for peak lateral acceleration and 8,000 RPM engagement.",
